A speech by Xi Jinping, general secretary of the Communist Party of China (CPC) Central Committee, on learning from the history to create a better future was published Saturday. The speech by Xi, also Chinese president and chairman of the Central Military Commission, was published in this year's first issue of the Qiushi Journal, a flagship magazine of the CPC Central Committee. (Cover: An exterior view of the Museum of the Communist Party of China in Beijing, China, June 22, 2021. /Xinhua)